    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "第三个画X的地方，要下进一条沟。大队的人声彻底听不见了，只有他自己的喘。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "（最后一个。喊完拿钱。……叫、叫啥来着？）",
      "next": "c1"
    },
    "c1": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "wrong_a",
          "text": "「黄丙文——」",
          "next": "fb_wrong"
        },
        {
          "id": "wrong_b",
          "text": "「王秉文——」",
          "next": "fb_wrong"
        },
        {
          "id": "right",
          "text": "「黄秉文——」",
          "next": "fb_right"
        },
        {
          "id": "skip",
          "text": "（黑成这样……不喊了。几个铜板，不挣了。）",
          "next": "fb_skip"
        }
      ]
    },
    "fb_right": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "喊完，林子里像有什么「醒了」——宿鸟惊飞，枝叶无风自动。他心里一阵发毛。",
      "next": "sig_right"
    },
